# Project Index Maintenance

When adding, moving, deleting, or materially changing project files, update `PROJECT_INDEX.md` in the repo root if the change affects how an AI agent should navigate or understand the project.

Keep updates lean:

- Add path, purpose, and when to read.
- Remove stale paths.
- Update the structure tree for important directories and files.
- Do not paste large file summaries; link by path and describe the role.
